Dracos:
 
Looks off in the direction that he traveled to the Maximal Base. "Odd as it seems there are some things out there that I am not aprivilaged to say. But one thing I can say is that this question you ask is hard for me to answer." Dracos sifts his weight slightly," I am not from here yet I am. I was around for a while but then I lost my memory.and where I was found there sure are more. But one thing I can say is that I have no qurrals with you. But the one that is holding this planet hostage. I don't belong to any facction out there. I am a Mercenary. Well lets just say we are."
Dracos lifts up his  Left Arm To Reveal a Gestalt Junction Point. "How this fully works I am not sure."
